Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.04,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（时空幻境之永恒传奇  1）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾发生过战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后被称为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.41,0:00:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“极光战争”的这场战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.55,0:00:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生在赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和茵费利亚之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛雷斯提亚便断绝交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.43,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.20,0:00:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个世界面临即将灭亡的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.10,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出来拯救这场危机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是一群无名的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.36,0:02:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1话  对面世界的冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.73,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.97,0:02:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得最近怪怪的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.87,0:02:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.24,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有很注意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的怪怪的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许将会发生什么事也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发生什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,譬如说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.68,0:02:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.65,0:02:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从赛雷斯提亚掉下来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别讲的那么高兴啦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是赛雷斯提亚耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有东西掉下来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁定会造成大灾难的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经有两千年没有交流了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.83,0:02:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…法拉快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.94,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷西斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.34,0:02:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.71,0:02:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…梅露蒂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉你要不要紧哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.99,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说了些梦话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好担心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我做了场梦啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可怕的梦吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我做的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次遇到梅露蒂时的情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在仔细回想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.47,0:03:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是从那时候开始的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才遇到她就是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的语言根本就无法沟通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.99,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这里太危险  快带她离开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.59,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问为什么啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的事我也还记忆犹新呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的语言不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂真的好困扰哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  里德！你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.15,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么…就是看天空啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不改老样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样躺着仰望天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就无法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要发生大崩落呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有可能发生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的认知未免太松懈了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面世界的茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.54,0:04:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断的越来越接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后发生冲撞的现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大崩落…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.71,0:04:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会在不久的将来发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.32,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那是由观测所得到的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我相信不久在学术上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也会受到承认的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  明兹大学光晶灵学部里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑最优秀的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔·查伊贝尔非常有信心的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是  我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会像现在这样出来旅行的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就休息到这儿  准备出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德·哈谢尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.21,0:05:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉·奥尔斯达特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔·查伊贝尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.32,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跟那些人一起旅行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.67,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在那之前她从哪里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么到这大地的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那些人的目标是法罗斯山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为法罗斯那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说有光之大晶灵的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而水之大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之大晶灵以及风之大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已经跟他们一起行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要对他们展开行动？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有不少的好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们准备吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂你负责去取水来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔和里德你们去找柴火…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  里德？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有人在盯着我们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一进森林里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有自己变成猎物的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是大型野兽或怪物之类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这气氛跟被那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上的时候一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是猎师高手的第六感吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个人的专长是在学问方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于学术上无法证明的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一概都不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…你大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为长途旅行太劳累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  没了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.04,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋熊的肉干不见了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说要在今天吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以预先留下来的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不关梅露蒂的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种偷吃东西的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是绝不会做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.32,0:07:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.92,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为昨天半夜我肚子超饿一把的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想说只吃一口就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟然那么好吃就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直叮咛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准偷吃东西的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.68,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个人…从以前就是那样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉  够…够了啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你气也差不多该消了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦  我向你道歉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.44,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个要不要紧哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.92,0:08:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死我了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧，法拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德  这是拿人家当垫背的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说的话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啦  别这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用解释！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉赢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是被他打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~母亲般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~油菜花啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.55,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是遇上了进退两难的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的年轻的旅人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~母亲般的…好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想到要说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就把舌头给咬下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉那家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有找到晚餐的猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不准你回来  知不知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉~真是有够麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.95,0:09:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现今晚晚餐了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再给你最后一击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.01,0:10:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  为什么我会毫发无伤呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.50,0:10:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.94,0:10:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心后面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼~好险好险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厉害哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德怎么去那么久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是跑到哪里闲逛去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂快饿死了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连我都快敌不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿得痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  我去找吃的回来好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个在这里等我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫可莉娜·索鲁珍特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个美丽的吟游诗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下名垂青史的诗歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我毕生的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚看到你的刀法时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有个想法闪过我的脑子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来一定会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.70,0:11:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名垂青史的伟大人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我便有了这样的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.77,0:11:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能创作出名垂青史的诗歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.98,0:11:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于这样的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我待在你身边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.28,0:11:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你如此年轻有为的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让我待在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.73,0:12:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你给我听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会当名垂青史的大人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没那个意思当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算待在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.21,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写出名垂青史的诗歌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为了答谢你的救命之恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供你一点不错的情报吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的情报？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.91,0:12:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.68,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常适合当今天的晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚餐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受诅咒的沼泽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  在那个沼泽里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栖息了一种以人类为饵食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫死亡螃蟹的怪物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那种怪物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会使用小型怪物来当诱饵呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.17,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以千万不能接近沼泽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我会小心一点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么告辞了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受诅咒的沼泽啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德和法拉怎么都去那么久啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.59,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人到底在搞什么鬼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.09,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天啊  法拉跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他梦到跟梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见面时的梦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.33,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  法拉他做了那种梦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…第一次见面的时候啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带他来找基尔你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希望你能帮帮梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像只会说晶灵语而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.79,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请你设法帮忙翻译啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说晶灵语？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底是什么来头啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到赛雷斯提亚人会从天而降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还跟大晶灵缔结契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想设法阻止大崩落的发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看大学里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.57,0:14:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁定没半个会相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  你想回大学去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在看过所有一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并证实我的理论之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.61,0:14:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塞菲亚德环内的黑体之危险性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来自列雷特球的能源歪曲这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说已经是非常确定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要查明大崩落得发生原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了从法罗斯山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡过光之桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到赛雷斯提亚之外别无他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你听的懂吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔说的话常让我受益良多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德你回来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思这么晚才回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  法拉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你已经无路可逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.09,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的晚餐先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.23,0:15:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你也想拿我当晚餐哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可是不会输的哟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌底破！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了  挺有效的样子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因就是那样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受阻咒的沼泽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那法拉不就有危险了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之得快点找到法拉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双撞掌底破！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连牙弹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点用都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.99,0:16:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔神剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.13,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是对付小喽啰而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.30,0:17:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可一点都不像你哟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太饿了  所以使不上力气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这很像你没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.54,0:17:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.31,0:17:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉！  后面就交给我们吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.98,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.15,0:17:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵吉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  召唤大晶灵吧\N好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾水之医治来保护汝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.77,0:17:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊弗力特  西尔夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.91,0:17:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾之炙热魔掌熔化为灰烬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.42,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空之风啊降下来并化为龙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮拜托你啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.06,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来似乎具有水的属性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是掌管水的力量的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连攻击力都会减半吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  基尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之大晶灵西尔夫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与火之大晶灵伊弗力特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同赐予我力量吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.01,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不咧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你…你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.65,0:18:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说“请”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有求于人时应该要加个请字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你们这些人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.89,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尔夫  伊弗力特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没时间这样闹着玩哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都听不懂这种笑话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你讲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风刀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.37,0:18:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.61,0:18:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.01,0:18:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎牙破斩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这告诉你别太小看我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德！干掉他了耶  里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你们不吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐的话刚才里德他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.54,0:19:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…该怎么说呢  那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.78,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没食欲啦  对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对对对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们已经先吃过的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要说出来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.52,0:19:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被法拉知道我们没等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就径自先吃饱的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你们在看什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.93,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦  那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.96,0:19:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是怎么了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽量吃就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德·哈谢尔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那条命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.08,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我玛萝妮·布鲁卡诺要定了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔神剑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.22,0:20:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的这一名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称是玛萝妮的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.96,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的真实身份到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德他们的命运将会如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.23,0:20:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待下回精彩好戏


